trans-unit.source: Provides the base implementation for all controls that contain single content and have a header.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller grundläggande implementeringen för alla kontroller som enda innehåll och har ett sidhuvud.

trans-unit.source: HeaderedContentControl inherits the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> property from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl> and defines the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> property that is of type <xref:System.Object>.
trans-unit.target: HeaderedContentControl ärver <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>Egenskaper från <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>och definierar den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>egenskap som är av typen <xref:System.Object>.</xref:System.Object> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> provides a heading for the control.

Like the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> can be any type.
trans-unit.target: Som det <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>-egenskapen för en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>kan ha olika typer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows two <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem> objects, which inherit from HeaderedContentControl.
trans-unit.target: Följande bild visar två <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem>objekt som ärver från HeaderedContentControl.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem>

trans-unit.source: The first <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem> has <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> objects as the content in both the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>: the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> is set to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel> that contains an <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Ellipse> and a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>; the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> is set to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel> that contains a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> and a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Label>.
trans-unit.target: Först <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem>har <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>objekt som innehåll i både den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>anges till ett <xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel>värde som innehåller en <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Ellipse>och en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>som <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>har angetts till ett <xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel>värde som innehåller en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>och en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Label>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Label> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> </xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Ellipse> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.StackPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> of the second <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem> is set to a string and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> is set to a single <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>Den andra <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem>är en sträng och <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>anges till en enda <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>

trans-unit.source: ![TabControl](~/add/media/controlcontentmodelteabitem.PNG "TabControl") TabControl with different types in the Header property A HeaderedContentControl has a limited default style.
trans-unit.target: ![TabControl](~/add/media/controlcontentmodelteabitem.PNG "TabControl") TabControl med olika typer i egenskapen Rubrik A HeaderedContentControl har en begränsad standardformatet.

trans-unit.source: An application developer can create a HeaderedContentControl, but its appearance will be very simple.
trans-unit.target: En programutvecklare kan skapa en HeaderedContentControl men utseendet kan enkelt.

trans-unit.source: If you wish to enhance the appearance of the control, you can create a new <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill förbättra utseendet på kontrollen kan du skapa en ny <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: A HeaderedContentControl is useful for creating custom controls because it provides a model for single content controls with headers.
trans-unit.target: En HeaderedContentControl är användbart för att skapa anpassade kontroller eftersom det ger en modell för enskild innehållskontroller med rubriker.

trans-unit.source: Dependency properties for this control might be set by the control’s default style.
trans-unit.target: Beroendeegenskaper för den här kontrollen kan ställas in av kontrollens standardformat.

trans-unit.source: If a property is set by a default style, the property might change from its default value when the control appears in the application.
trans-unit.target: Om en egenskapen anges av ett standardformat kan egenskapen ändras från standardvärdet när kontrollen visas i programmet.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
trans-unit.target: Standardformatet som bestäms av vilka tema används när programmet körs.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Default WPF Themes](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).
